flowchart LR
    ClientAgent[External Coding Agent]
    Strategy[CGFirstQueryStrategy]
    MCPTools[ContextGraph MCP Tools]
    Registry[GraphRegistry]
    Graph[(Project FalkorDB Graph)]
    Cache[(Redis Query Cache)]
    Trace[(Trace Recorder and Evaluator)]
    LocalFallback[Local Snippet Fallback]
    Producer[MCPProducer]
    Queue[(Redis Jobs Stream)]
    Consumer[IndexerConsumer]
    Pipeline[IndexPipeline]
    Repo[Repository Files]

    ClientAgent -->|query| Strategy
    Strategy -->|retrieve_context and call graph| MCPTools
    Strategy -->|fallback when graph quality is low| LocalFallback

    MCPTools --> Cache
    MCPTools --> Registry
    MCPTools --> Trace
    Registry --> Graph

    MCPTools -->|index requests| Producer
    Producer --> Queue
    Consumer --> Queue
    Consumer --> Pipeline
    Pipeline --> Repo
    Pipeline --> Registry

    Trace -->|quality signals| Strategy
    Graph -->|symbol and edge context| Strategy
    Cache -->|warm reads| Strategy
    LocalFallback -->|bounded code snippets| ClientAgent
    MCPTools -->|final graph-backed context| ClientAgent
